Title: Frontend frameworks are useful
Description:
I thought that all frontend frameworks are bloat after being unhappy with the direction taken by React.
I feel very different today. I just moved Imgbar, my side project, from JavaScript to Svelte.
Imgbar Imgbar is an image editor for inserting text into images, inspired by Imgflip. The first version of the project was made with Sinatra and SQLite on the server, JavaScript in the browser. I also used htmx for implementing the search feature.
